creator: TPARK
descriptionHtml:
It’s simple, safe and convenient. Now you have a „smart parking meter” in your pocket, and you can extend your parking time wherever you are: at the office, at the coffee-shop or in the cinema.

Pay for parking via SMS with TPARK in just 3 stepts:
1. Enter you plate number
2. Select the city and the parking area
3. Touch „PARK” button.

You get notified 5 minutes before parking expires, so you can extend it from anywhere.

***
You can now buy the vouchers for parking in Timișoara and Oradea by beep/voucher directly from the TPARK app using the credit card. After completing the transaction, you will receive the voucher code and and payment details.via e-mail.

***

TPARK offers you the newest way to pay the parking fee - payment by card. The service is available in more than 30 cities, the payment is made in just a few seconds, and those who pay the parking with the card will receive the transaction data and the invoice by e-mail.

***
Are you planning a trip to Hungary? You can buy the vignette using TPARK app (for vehicles with a maximum permissible gross weight of 3.5 tons) and you can also pay for parking in Hungary using the credit card. In addition, you will receive via email a notification that reminds you when the vignette expires.

***
Furthermore, TPARK gives you more great features, thus driving remains one of the daily pleasures.
➲ you can add several cars
➲ you can see the list of payment options for each city and the charge fee each parking area
➲ START/STOP beep parking in Timișoara and Oradea:
➲ automatically send SMS with the plate number and the area parking code selected
➲ receive parking confirmation for via SMS (displays SMS confirmation message);
➲ you can pay the parking fines in over 10 cities across Romania
➲ you can pay the tax for Fetești-Cernavodă bridge
➲ you can buy vignette for any type of vehicle
➲ you receive notifications (audio, vibration or both options)
➲ automatic updates

It’s simple, safe and convenient. Now you have a „smart parking meter” in your pocket, and you can extend your parking time wherever you are: at the office, at the coffee-shop or in the cinema.

Pay for parking via SMS with TPARK in just 3 stepts:
1. Enter you plate number
2. Select the city and the parking area
3. Touch „PARK” button.

You get notified 5 minutes before parking expires, so you can extend it from anywhere.

***
You can now buy the vouchers for parking in Timișoara and Oradea by beep/voucher directly from the TPARK app using the credit card. After completing the transaction, you will receive the voucher code and and payment details.via e-mail.

***

TPARK offers you the newest way to pay the parking fee - payment by card. The service is available in more than 40 cities, the payment is made in just a few seconds, and those who pay the parking with the card will receive the transaction data and the invoice by e-mail.

***
Are you planning a trip to Hungary? You can buy the vignette using TPARK app (for vehicles with a maximum permissible gross weight of 3.5 tons) and you can also pay for parking in Hungary using the credit card. In addition, you will receive via email a notification that reminds you when the vignette expires.

***
Furthermore, TPARK gives you more great features, thus driving remains one of the daily pleasures.
➲ you can add several cars
➲ you can see the list of payment options for each city and the charge fee each parking area
➲ START/STOP beep parking in Timișoara and Oradea:
➲ automatically send SMS with the plate number and the area parking code selected
➲ receive parking confirmation for via SMS (displays SMS confirmation message);
➲ you can pay the parking fines in over 10 cities across Romania
➲ you can pay the tax for Fetești-Cernavodă bridge
➲ you can buy vignette for any type of vehicle
➲ you receive notifications (audio, vibration or both options)
➲ automatic updates
descriptionShort: Parking and e-vignette mobile payment. SMART PARKING!

descriptionHtml:
It’s simple, safe and convenient. Now you have a „smart parking meter” in your pocket, and you can extend your parking time wherever you are: at the office, at the coffee-shop or in the cinema.

Pay for parking via SMS with TPARK in just 3 stepts:
1. Enter you plate number
2. Select the city and the parking area
3. Touch „PARK” button.

You get notified 5 minutes before parking expires, so you can extend it from anywhere. The parking payment is available in over 55 cities in Romania (Alba Iulia, Alexandria, Arad, Bacau, Baia Mare, Bistrita, Botosani, Brasov, Buzau, Baile Felix/1 Mai, Baile Herculane, Cluj Napoca, Constanta, Corabia, Craiova, Campulung Moldovenesc, Campulung Muscel, Dej, Deva, Dorohoi, Drobeta Turnu Severin, Focsani, Falticeni, Galati, Huedin, Iasi, Jibou, Mamaia, Mangalia, Medias, Odorheiu Secuiesc, Oradea, Piatra Neamt, Pitesti, Ploiesti, Reghin, Roman, Ramnicu Sarat, Ramnicu Valcea, Satu Mare, Sfantu Gheorghe, Sibiu, Sighetu Marmatiei, Sighisoara, Slanic Moldova, Sovata, Statiuni litoral, Suceava, Tecuci, Timisoara, Turda, Targu Jiu, Targu Neamt, Targu Secuiesc, Tirgu Mures, Vatra Dornei, Zalau).

***
Are you planning a trip to Hungary? You can buy the vignette using TPARK app (for vehicles with a maximum permissible gross weight of 3.5 tons) and you can also pay for parking in Hungary using the credit card. In addition, you will receive via email a notification that reminds you when the vignette expires.

***
Furthermore, TPARK gives you more great features, thus driving remains one of the daily pleasures.
➲ you can add several cars
➲ you can see the list of payment options for each city and the charge fee each parking area
➲ START/STOP beep parking in Timișoara and Oradea:
➲ automatically send SMS with the plate number and the area parking code selected
➲ receive parking confirmation for via SMS (displays SMS confirmation message);
➲ you can pay the parking fines in over 10 cities across Romania
➲ you can pay the tax for Fetești-Cernavodă bridge
➲ you can buy vignette for any type of vehicle
➲ you receive notifications (audio, vibration or both options)
➲ automatic updates
descriptionShort: Parking and e-vignette mobile payment. SMART PARKING!
